## Design
- Style: Modern + industrial (clean layout, strong typography, steel/industrial colour tones)
- Home: hero → product family cards (3 families) → company intro → services overview → contact CTA
- Pages: Home, Products (filterable by family), Product detail, About, Contact
- Product detail shows: image, main technical specs, features, applications, PDF download button, **Request Quote** CTA
- Use "Contact for Quote" CTA wording on product/family pages (no public pricing)
- For Y/YR product page, show: "Catalog available on request" + WhatsApp/contact-form CTA
